      "summary": "Rep. Russ Diamond's office announced it will hold regular pop-up office hours at two locations in his district — Palmyra on the first Wednesday of each month and Myerstown on the third Wednesday, both from 9 a.m. to noon. Staff will be available to help residents with state services such as vehicle registration and birth certificate requests. These sessions supplement his existing full-time office in Jonestown.",
      "action_type": "event",
